    <release version="0.10.1" revision="1" maintainer="Tobias Koch"
        email="tobias.koch@gmail.com" date="2014-11-29 19:41:00 +0200">
        <changeset>
            <li>fixes to exception handling</li>
            <li>runner.tcl: make sure reports always go to outdir</li>
            <li>Markdown: simplified "mailto:" code (Danyil Bohdan).</li>
            <li>Markdown: process email links w/ or w/o "mailto:" (Danyil Bohdan).</li>
            <li>Markdown: respect HTML comments (Danyil Bohdan).</li>
            <li>fix interference when launching subprocesses from different threads</li>
            <li>caius testplan exits with non-zero exit status when tests fail</li>
        </changeset>
    </release>
